# =============================================================================
# MAGNETO V4 -- .gitignore
# =============================================================================
# Two intents drive this file:
#   (1) Never commit operator-owned data (auth, users, schedules, history,
#       sessions, audit, rotation state). These are written by a running
#       MAGNETO instance and must stay private to that instance.
#   (2) Never commit local-only artifacts: logs, backups, update staging,
#       generated launcher scripts, IDE/tooling state, zip snapshots.
#
# Curated reference data (techniques.json, campaigns.json, nist-mappings.json,
# ttp-classification.json, builtin-ttp-ids.json) IS tracked because new users
# need it to bootstrap from a fresh release zip.
# =============================================================================

# --- Operator-owned runtime data (NEVER commit) ----------------------------
data/auth.json
data/users.json
data/sessions.json
data/schedules.json
data/smart-rotation.json
data/execution-history.json
data/audit-log.json

# --- Logs ------------------------------------------------------------------
logs/
magneto.log
*.log

# --- Update mechanism artifacts (generated locally, never committed) ------
backups/
update-staging/
Apply-Update.ps1
Run-Schedule.ps1
Run-SmartRotation.ps1

# --- Local archives / build outputs ---------------------------------------
*.zip
*.zip.old

# --- Tooling / IDE / OS ---------------------------------------------------
.claude/
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
Thumbs.db
.DS_Store

# --- Internal planning + customer-internal docs (never publish) -----------
.planning/
docs/892httpslogin.tailscale.comadmininv.txt

# --- Local tooling / AI assistant instructions (not part of distribution) -
CLAUDE.md
